{
  "stem": "10587.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't too far away, or maybe just a, a, a storage yard of, of, looked like stones and bricks and building material, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they told you to take you jacket off, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they gave you this pajama prison uniform with the stripes, and to reverse it, and put it-- put the back in the front and the front in the back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- and used to hold down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would pour in, or put in, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you would take it from one place and put it in another place, you know, and carry it in your--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stone, mainly stone, from one place-- you know, in, in your jacket, you know, whatever-- and put it someplace else, where somebody else would take it off.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or you-- sometimes, you would just drop it and go back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the kind of work I remember doing when I-- during the time I was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Constantly beating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Murder, [INAUDIBLE]--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shooting, rifle butts, kicking, and lot of bashing people on the head with their rifle butts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And how you constantly heard this, you [GERMAN SPEECH], you shitty Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in this-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the evening when we came back, you lined up again for food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and you got a, you know, with the ladle, they, they would.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you ate real quick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- first time is shame on me, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- and my father said, eat everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always, he said, eat everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I realized really why he said it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I'll tell you the story later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and this is like a constant.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
